150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s directly dive into bedroom cupboard design ideas that can give your personal space a trendy makeover. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Built-In Modern Bedroom Cupboard<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This six-door cupboard is built into the wall to provide you with extra space in your bedroom. It stands tall from the floor to ceiling making this room look airy, open, and breathes elegance into this room. It perfectly complements the brown-toned veneer floor tiles. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004720\/bedroom-design-cupboard-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Maximize space with wall-integrated bedroom cupboards. Explore modern bedroom cupboard designs for extra storage!\" class=\"wp-image-5619\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004720\/bedroom-design-cupboard-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004720\/bedroom-design-cupboard-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004720\/bedroom-design-cupboard-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004720\/bedroom-design-cupboard-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Embrace a clutter free life with functional wardrobe designs\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16114642\/clutter-free-life-with-functional-wardrobe-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Corner Cupboard for Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make efficient use of those awkward corners that are often overlooked in your room with these corner-styled cupboards. You can use every inch of the space and accommodate all you want in a neat and organised fashion with this design. This corner cupboard also comes with a side-closed cabinet with multiple shelves where you can store smaller and more delicate items. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004739\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom cupboard design where corners that are often overlooked\" class=\"wp-image-5624\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004739\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004739\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004739\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004739\/modern-bedroom-cupboard-designs-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-wardrobe-designs-for-bedroom\/\">Modern Wardrobe Designs For Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Four-Door Sliding Bedroom Cupboard<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This four-door sliding cupboard is one of the best designs to save space since they are really easy to use, look modern, stylish and luxurious. Spread across an entire wall, this design also frees up floor space so you can easily move around your bedroom without any hindrance. A metallic door handle also gives you a good grip. It is the perfect addition to a beautiful modular house.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004704\/bedroom-cupboard-design-or-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom cupboard design to save space since they are really easy to use and also check out these cupboard interior designs\" class=\"wp-image-5615\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004704\/bedroom-cupboard-design-or-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004704\/bedroom-cupboard-design-or-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004704\/bedroom-cupboard-design-or-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004704\/bedroom-cupboard-design-or-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Sliding Wardrobe Designs for Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Plywood Cupboard For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for a cheaper alternative to wood in terms of budget, opt for this 3&#215;1 plywood cupboard. Fine finishes and earthy coloured doors go well with the decor of this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom\u2019s interiors<\/a>. You can choose from among a wide variety of designs that can be directly laminated onto the cupboard itself. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004657\/6-door-cupboard-design-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Explore modern bedroom cupboard designs with fine finishes and earthy-colored doors that complement your decor\" class=\"wp-image-5613\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004657\/6-door-cupboard-design-for-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004657\/6-door-cupboard-design-for-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004657\/6-door-cupboard-design-for-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004657\/6-door-cupboard-design-for-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Cupboard With An Attached Dressing Table for Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to cut down on time running back and forth from one corner of your room to the other to ace the perfect look (clothes+grooming), then design a bedroom cupboard with an attached dressing table. Place all your cosmetic, beauty and grooming products neatly into various drawers provided.&nbsp; They are quite trendy, popular and in-demand. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004713\/bedroom-cupboard-designs-photos.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom cupboard designs photos which are quite trendy and popular in demand \" class=\"wp-image-5617\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004713\/bedroom-cupboard-designs-photos.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004713\/bedroom-cupboard-designs-photos-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004713\/bedroom-cupboard-designs-photos-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004713\/bedroom-cupboard-designs-photos-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Explore About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/dressing-cupboard-design\/\">Dressing Cupboard Designs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cupboard With An Attached Study Table For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This cupboard with an attached study table is a great choice for a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/how-to-shape-your-kids-mood-with-colors\/\">kid\u2019s bedroom<\/a> since they need maximum storage for their toys, clothes, shoes. Apart from this they require a dedicated space for reading, writing and assignments. Long and open shelves, drawers and the sea green-beige tone of this cupboard makes this bedroom\u2019s interior look more creative, energetic and attractive. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004724\/cupboard-images-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom cupboard design with an attached study table for bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-5620\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004724\/cupboard-images-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004724\/cupboard-images-bedroom-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004724\/cupboard-images-bedroom-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004724\/cupboard-images-bedroom-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Cupboard With Built-In Mirror For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a cupboard with a built-in mirror to your bedroom to instantly glam up your space. These mirrors help reflect light to every corner of your room, thus making it look bigger and brighter. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004716\/bedroom-cupboard-ideas-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom cupboard design ideas where mirrors help reflect light to every corner of your room for bedroom cupboard interior design\" class=\"wp-image-5618\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004716\/bedroom-cupboard-ideas-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004716\/bedroom-cupboard-ideas-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004716\/bedroom-cupboard-ideas-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004716\/bedroom-cupboard-ideas-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decorative Laminate Cupboard<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This decorative laminate cupboard looks classy and adds a bold statement to your bedroom space. Its unique design is trendy and eye-catching. Decorative laminates are popular and available in several finishes so you can choose any of them to complement your d\u00e9cor. Also, they are extremely scratch-resistant and super easy to clean with a cloth.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004700\/bedroom-cupboard-colours-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom cupboard design colours which ooks classy and adds a bold statement and also check out these cupboard colours for bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-5614\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004700\/bedroom-cupboard-colours-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp