<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Is your wardrobe placed right?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16140947\/wardrobe-placed-right.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Narrow Cupboard By The Window<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>These white narrow cupboards accompanied by multiple drawers on either side of the bedroom window, definitely bring in coastal and sea-side vibes into the interiors. A low seating area in between the cupboard adds freshness and light to space. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004735\/fancy-bedroom-cupboard-doors-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"modern bedroom cupboard design for a narrow cupboard by the window\" class=\"wp-image-5623\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004735\/fancy-bedroom-cupboard-doors-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004735\/fancy-bedroom-cupboard-doors-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004735\/fancy-bedroom-cupboard-doors-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21004735\/fancy-bedroom-cupboard-doors-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wooden Bedroom Cupboard<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This solid wooden cupboard is a perfect blend of versatility and durability. It suits the theme of almost any style of bedroom interiors &#8211; traditional or modern. Wood adds a charming element to bedrooms since it emits warm and earthy vibes. Though wood is more expensive than other materials, it becomes as good as new if it is given a good coat of polish. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" s